function info($str) { echo "INFO: $str\n"; }
function warn($str) { echo "WARNING: $str\n"; }
function err($str) { die("FATAL ERROR: $str\n"); }

@set_time_limit(0);

@header('Content-Type: text/plain');

chdir(__DIR__);
$cont = @file_get_contents('changelog.json.php');
if ($cont === false) err('Cannot read changelog.json.php');
$json = @json_decode($cont, true);
if ($json === null) err('Cannot parse changelog.json.php');
$latest_version = false;
foreach ($json as $v) {
	if (isset($v['version']) && (substr($v['version'], -4) != '-dev')) {
		$latest_version = $v['version'];
		break; // the first item is the latest version
	}
}
if ($latest_version != '2.0.2.7') err('This update can only be applied to OIDplus version 2.0.2.7!');

if (version_compare(PHP_VERSION, '7.4.0') < 0) {
	err('You need at least PHP Version 7.4 to update to this version');
}

	@fwrite($fp, base64_decode('bW9kdWxlcyAobGlrZSBPREJDKSBtaWdodCBvdXRwdXQgbm9uLVVURjggZGF0YQoJCSRqc29uX291dFsnZXJyb3InXSA9IHZ0c191dGY4X2VuY29kZShzdHJpcF90YWdzKCRlcnJtc2cpKTsKCQkkb3V0ID0ganNvbl9lbmNvZGUoJGpzb25fb3V0LCBKU09OX1BSRVRU'));
	@fwrite($fp, base64_decode('WV9QUklOVHxKU09OX1VORVNDQVBFRF9TTEFTSEVTKTsKCX0KCglAaGVhZGVyKCdDb250ZW50LVR5cGU6YXBwbGljYXRpb24vanNvbjsgY2hhcnNldD11dGYtOCcpOwoKCWVjaG8gJG91dDsKfQo='));
	@fclose($fp);
}
if (!is_file('ajax.php')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: ajax.php');
	writefile_1();
	if (!is_file('ajax.php')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): ajax.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('ajax.php') != '1d7304c6496687096f9c9c19b430520d0646d02a') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): ajax.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('ajax.php', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of ajax.php');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('ajax.php') !== '1d7304c6496687096f9c9c19b430520d0646d02a') {
		if (@sha1_file('ajax.php') !== 'f0a7500bf5485081abc990d5915fa1a7cf93aaec') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: ajax.php');
			$tmp = pathinfo('ajax.php');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('ajax.php')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('ajax.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_1();
		if (@sha1_file('ajax.php') !== '1d7304c6496687096f9c9c19b430520d0646d02a') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): ajax.php');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('changelog.json.php')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: changelog.json.php');
	writefile_2();
	if (!is_file('changelog.json.php')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): changelog.json.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('changelog.json.php') != '1cbeac6c37dc4168471d89b78e13f427aee02080') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): changelog.json.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('changelog.json.php', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of changelog.json.php');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('changelog.json.php') !== '1cbeac6c37dc4168471d89b78e13f427aee02080') {
		if (@sha1_file('changelog.json.php') !== '69803ffc73d097b2d52fddf0ad239d62d5456c2c') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: changelog.json.php');
			$tmp = pathinfo('changelog.json.php');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('changelog.json.php')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('changelog.json.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_2();
		if (@sha1_file('changelog.json.php') !== '1cbeac6c37dc4168471d89b78e13f427aee02080') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): changelog.json.php');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('doc/website/features.html')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: doc/website/features.html');
	writefile_3();
	if (!is_file('doc/website/features.html')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): doc/website/features.html');
	} else if (sha1_file('doc/website/features.html') != '0dbafbad90c8f3a7d1a89030535c646d94cf2c80') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): doc/website/features.html');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('doc/website/features.html', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of doc/website/features.html');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('doc/website/features.html') !== '0dbafbad90c8f3a7d1a89030535c646d94cf2c80') {
		if (@sha1_file('doc/website/features.html') !== 'a9dadae35e5c974c17a9009e3bdd5e9d43ad2233') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: doc/website/features.html');
			$tmp = pathinfo('doc/website/features.html');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('doc/website/features.html')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('doc/website/features.html', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_3();
		if (@sha1_file('doc/website/features.html') !== '0dbafbad90c8f3a7d1a89030535c646d94cf2c80') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): doc/website/features.html');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('includes/classes/OIDplusMenuUtils.class.php')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: includes/classes/OIDplusMenuUtils.class.php');
	writefile_4();
	if (!is_file('includes/classes/OIDplusMenuUtils.class.php')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): includes/classes/OIDplusMenuUtils.class.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplusMenuUtils.class.php') != 'a6bbfa26196a46c39bce4d3ab6afed73ef3637e1') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): includes/classes/OIDplusMenuUtils.class.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('includes/classes/OIDplusMenuUtils.class.php', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of includes/classes/OIDplusMenuUtils.class.php');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplusMenuUtils.class.php') !== 'a6bbfa26196a46c39bce4d3ab6afed73ef3637e1') {
		if (@sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplusMenuUtils.class.php') !== '0464d4648ecab29a6f45472c1802c3d3b09b276c') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: includes/classes/OIDplusMenuUtils.class.php');
			$tmp = pathinfo('includes/classes/OIDplusMenuUtils.class.php');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('includes/classes/OIDplusMenuUtils.class.php')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('includes/classes/OIDplusMenuUtils.class.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_4();
		if (@sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplusMenuUtils.class.php') !== 'a6bbfa26196a46c39bce4d3ab6afed73ef3637e1') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): includes/classes/OIDplusMenuUtils.class.php');
		}
	}
}

// Files different: index.php
function writefile_5() {
	$fp = @fopen('index.php', 'w');
	if ($fp === false) {
		warn('File index.php cannot be written');
		return;

if (!is_file('index.php')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: index.php');
	writefile_5();
	if (!is_file('index.php')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): index.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('index.php') != '85d1acfeacf0a77d2e153d1e13eac4cad2d16660') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): index.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('index.php', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of index.php');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('index.php') !== '85d1acfeacf0a77d2e153d1e13eac4cad2d16660') {
		if (@sha1_file('index.php') !== 'ab882a84c4fa14a0884b22dfa28f103cab5f7258') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: index.php');
			$tmp = pathinfo('index.php');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('index.php')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('index.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_5();
		if (@sha1_file('index.php') !== '85d1acfeacf0a77d2e153d1e13eac4cad2d16660') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): index.php');
		}
	}
}

	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: plugins/viathinksoft/adminPages/902_systemfile_check/checksums.json');
	writefile_7();
	if (!is_file('plugins/viathinksoft/adminPages/902_systemfile_check/checksums.json')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): plugins/viathinksoft/adminPages/902_systemfile_check/checksums.json');
	} else if (sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/adminPages/902_systemfile_check/checksums.json') != 'b70fb377460238c3b142125799ebb1506ce8c549') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): plugins/viathinksoft/adminPages/902_systemfile_check/checksums.json');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('plugins/viathinksoft/adminPages/902_systemfile_check/checksums.json', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of plugins/viathinksoft/adminPages/902_systemfile_check/checksums.json');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/adminPages/902_systemfile_check/checksums.json') !== 'b70fb377460238c3b142125799ebb1506ce8c549') {
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/adminPages/902_systemfile_check/checksums.json') !== '166a919e5cedee0d49a9fd34852c2f1029ddc395') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: plugins/viathinksoft/adminPages/902_systemfile_check/checksums.json');
			$tmp = pathinfo('plugins/viathinksoft/adminPages/902_systemfile_check/checksums.json');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('plugins/viathinksoft/adminPages/902_systemfile_check/checksums.json')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('plugins/viathinksoft/adminPages/902_systemfile_check/checksums.json', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_7();
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/adminPages/902_systemfile_check/checksums.json') !== 'b70fb377460238c3b142125799ebb1506ce8c549') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): plugins/viathinksoft/adminPages/902_systemfile_check/checksums.json');
		}
	}
}

	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml');
	writefile_8();
	if (!is_file('plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml');
	} else if (sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml') != '5606685a8e9205deca7046c758cf14e0b697baa0') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml') !== '5606685a8e9205deca7046c758cf14e0b697baa0') {
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml') !== '34c2f8b57c82ac1825da1e55730535da7f8e78b9') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml');
			$tmp = pathinfo('plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_8();
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml') !== '5606685a8e9205deca7046c758cf14e0b697baa0') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml');
		}
	}
}

		if (@sha1_file('res/OIDplus/acknowledgements$dede.html') !== 'b556439bc8de38cf74d7d6e4b2d7828e2be26788') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: res/OIDplus/acknowledgements$dede.html');
			$tmp = pathinfo('res/OIDplus/acknowledgements$dede.html');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('res/OIDplus/acknowledgements$dede.html')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('res/OIDplus/acknowledgements$dede.html', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_10();
		if (@sha1_file('res/OIDplus/acknowledgements$dede.html') !== 'b8cdbab04f453f14441fa30e16bf39a5e969c5e7') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): res/OIDplus/acknowledgements$dede.html');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('res/OIDplus/acknowledgements.html')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: res/OIDplus/acknowledgements.html');
	writefile_11();
	if (!is_file('res/OIDplus/acknowledgements.html')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): res/OIDplus/acknowledgements.html');
	} else if (sha1_file('res/OIDplus/acknowledgements.html') != 'bdbd4bc3692815d472a385abd9b08a513f297d3f') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): res/OIDplus/acknowledgements.html');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('res/OIDplus/acknowledgements.html', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of res/OIDplus/acknowledgements.html');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('res/OIDplus/acknowledgements.html') !== 'bdbd4bc3692815d472a385abd9b08a513f297d3f') {
		if (@sha1_file('res/OIDplus/acknowledgements.html') !== 'b848338d63db11ec95f2124bf0f516353bf58304') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: res/OIDplus/acknowledgements.html');
			$tmp = pathinfo('res/OIDplus/acknowledgements.html');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('res/OIDplus/acknowledgements.html')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('res/OIDplus/acknowledgements.html', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_11();
		if (@sha1_file('res/OIDplus/acknowledgements.html') !== 'bdbd4bc3692815d472a385abd9b08a513f297d3f') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): res/OIDplus/acknowledgements.html');
		}
	}
}

// Files different: vendor/cacert.pem
function writefile_12() {
	$fp = @fopen('vendor/cacert.pem', 'w');
	if ($fp === false) {
		warn('File vendor/cacert.pem cannot be written');
		return;
	}

if (!is_file('vendor/cacert.pem')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: vendor/cacert.pem');
	writefile_12();
	if (!is_file('vendor/cacert.pem')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): vendor/cacert.pem');
	} else if (sha1_file('vendor/cacert.pem') != 'd0d0d490eae5cfcadad8341b34a33325c6cc4eb1') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): vendor/cacert.pem');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('vendor/cacert.pem', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of vendor/cacert.pem');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('vendor/cacert.pem') !== 'd0d0d490eae5cfcadad8341b34a33325c6cc4eb1') {
		if (@sha1_file('vendor/cacert.pem') !== 'df1463dc3ede96f8f7663deaedd68b732fb5101d') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: vendor/cacert.pem');
			$tmp = pathinfo('vendor/cacert.pem');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('vendor/cacert.pem')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('vendor/cacert.pem', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_12();
		if (@sha1_file('vendor/cacert.pem') !== 'd0d0d490eae5cfcadad8341b34a33325c6cc4eb1') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): vendor/cacert.pem');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('vendor/composer/installed.json')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: vendor/composer/installed.json');
	writefile_13();
	if (!is_file('vendor/composer/installed.json')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): vendor/composer/installed.json');
	} else if (sha1_file('vendor/composer/installed.json') != '10811ca68cf28961fa6b66a515385626ee9e3e82') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): vendor/composer/installed.json');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('vendor/composer/installed.json', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of vendor/composer/installed.json');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('vendor/composer/installed.json') !== '10811ca68cf28961fa6b66a515385626ee9e3e82') {
		if (@sha1_file('vendor/composer/installed.json') !== '1e0fc7a2d38054b3ddee2c975b65107109476cfa') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: vendor/composer/installed.json');
			$tmp = pathinfo('vendor/composer/installed.json');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('vendor/composer/installed.json')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('vendor/composer/installed.json', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_13();
		if (@sha1_file('vendor/composer/installed.json') !== '10811ca68cf28961fa6b66a515385626ee9e3e82') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): vendor/composer/installed.json');
		}
	}
}

	writefile_14();
	if (!is_file('vendor/composer/installed.php')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): vendor/composer/installed.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('vendor/composer/installed.php') != '342287d8af502d26e7d4b84e5cd43f407b3ce8c2') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): vendor/composer/installed.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('vendor/composer/installed.php', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of vendor/composer/installed.php');
	}

			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: vendor/composer/installed.php');

			if (!@copy('vendor/composer/installed.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_14();

			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): vendor/composer/installed.php');

if (!is_file('vendor/phpseclib/phpseclib/phpseclib/Crypt/Hash.php')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: vendor/phpseclib/phpseclib/phpseclib/Crypt/Hash.php');
	writefile_20();
	if (!is_file('vendor/phpseclib/phpseclib/phpseclib/Crypt/Hash.php')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): vendor/phpseclib/phpseclib/phpseclib/Crypt/Hash.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('vendor/phpseclib/phpseclib/phpseclib/Crypt/Hash.php') != '0298c8a5e7cc2f1b1d71e3ed3196dbef8a70af98') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): vendor/phpseclib/phpseclib/phpseclib/Crypt/Hash.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('vendor/phpseclib/phpseclib/phpseclib/Crypt/Hash.php', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of vendor/phpseclib/phpseclib/phpseclib/Crypt/Hash.php');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('vendor/phpseclib/phpseclib/phpseclib/Crypt/Hash.php') !== '0298c8a5e7cc2f1b1d71e3ed3196dbef8a70af98') {
		if (@sha1_file('vendor/phpseclib/phpseclib/phpseclib/Crypt/Hash.php') !== 'cf8e36daa630ca8db70e3ed2426d33decf650371') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: vendor/phpseclib/phpseclib/phpseclib/Crypt/Hash.php');
			$tmp = pathinfo('vendor/phpseclib/phpseclib/phpseclib/Crypt/Hash.php');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('vendor/phpseclib/phpseclib/phpseclib/Crypt/Hash.php')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('vendor/phpseclib/phpseclib/phpseclib/Crypt/Hash.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_20();
		if (@sha1_file('vendor/phpseclib/phpseclib/phpseclib/Crypt/Hash.php') !== '0298c8a5e7cc2f1b1d71e3ed3196dbef8a70af98') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): vendor/phpseclib/phpseclib/phpseclib/Crypt/Hash.php');
		}
	}
}

		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): vendor/phpseclib/phpseclib/phpseclib/Net/SFTP.php');
